title: Bleed the Sky Discography (2004-2005)
description:
Bleed the Sky - Bleed the Sky (EP) (2004)
Bleed the Sky - Paradigm in Entropy (2005)

Bleed the Sky is a five-piece groove metal/metalcore group originating from Mission Viejo, California, currently signed to Nuclear Blast.

The band formed in January of 2003, consisting of vocalist Noah Robinson, guitarists Kyle Moorman and Wayne Miller, bassist Casey Kulek, and drummer Austin D&#039;Amond. The band signed a worldwide deal with Nuclear Blast on November 11, 2004.

The band&#039;s debut album, entitled Paradigm in Entropy, was released on April 19, 2005.
